passed away.)

548
01:05:17,120 --> 01:05:18,280
He passed away in the afternoon
of the day before yesterday.

549
01:05:18,600 --> 01:05:20,014
Should I attend the funeral or not?

550
01:05:20,677 --> 01:05:21,826
What are you going there for?

551
01:05:27,000 --> 01:05:29,240
Chen Li, thank you for helping me out.

552
01:05:29,240 --> 01:05:31,560
My roommate rented a house near the school.

553
01:05:31,560 --> 01:05:32,920
I'd better go stay with him.

554
01:05:32,920 --> 01:05:34,944
I think it would be
more convenient this way.

555
01:06:33,760 --> 01:06:34,760
I sprained my ankle.

556
01:06:34,760 --> 01:06:36,740
Shouldn't you check on me first
when you came in?

557
01:06:42,217 --> 01:06:44,412
Could you please take care
of my foot first?

558
01:06:51,030 --> 01:06:52,280
Stop looking around.

559
01:06:52,280 --> 01:06:53,561
I'm not hiding anyone.

560
01:06:54,520 --> 01:06:57,200
What are you doing here for no reason?

561
01:06:57,974 --> 01:07:00,134
I'm just helping to look after the store
when I don't have classes.

562
01:07:01,320 --> 01:07:02,960
I can't live in the house for free.

563
01:07:04,960 --> 01:07:06,240
Don't you live in the dormitory?

564
01:07:12,280 --> 01:07:13,440
This is the situation.

565
01:07:14,037 --> 01:07:15,960
There's always someone in the dorm
looking for trouble with me.

566
01:07:16,326 --> 01:07:17,451
I don't care about them.

567
01:07:17,476 --> 01:07:18,996
So I moved to my friend's place to live.

568
01:07:19,513 --> 01:07:22,092
Friend? Male or female?

569
01:07:33,120 --> 01:07:35,342
Don't attribute many things
to your own particularity.

570
01:07:35,572 --> 01:07:37,292
And don't think that
you're not good enough.

571
01:07:37,317 --> 01:07:39,069
Not everything can be perfect.

572
01:07:39,323 --> 01:07:41,443
And not everyone can get what they want.

573
01:07:41,468 --> 01:07:43,272
Just be what you are.

574
01:07:43,659 --> 01:07:45,499
Anything beyond that is not you.

575
01:07:45,963 --> 01:07:48,563
You are the best in your own world.

576
01:07:52,389 --> 01:07:56,175
(Two years later)

577
01:07:56,200 --> 01:07:57,400
You are asking me this?

578
01:07:57,840 --> 01:07:59,600
I thought you studied genetic engineering.

579
01:08:00,920 --> 01:08:04,360
From a genetic perspective, this is innate.

580
01:08:05,520 --> 01:08:06,920
However, for me,

581
01:08:07,769 --> 01:08:09,436
I'm not sure...

582
01:08:11,944 --> 01:08:13,680
whether this is a dependent
stress response or not.

583
01:08:14,120 --> 01:08:15,400
So you came to me.

584
01:08:16,094 --> 01:08:17,974
You can't get answers from other people.

585
01:08:18,097 --> 01:08:20,297
Because no one knows you better than you do.

586
01:08:21,360 --> 01:08:22,400
The reason you came to me

587
01:08:22,675 --> 01:08:26,162
is that you want to find some people to prove
that your views are correct.

588
01:08:26,802 --> 01:08:30,402
No matter what the result is,
it doesn't belong to you.

589
01:08:31,240 --> 01:08:32,680
I hope you can know.

590
01:08:33,520 --> 01:08:35,840
Besides seeking the definition
and approval of others,

591
01:08:35,840 --> 01:08:37,240
there is another way to go.

592
01:08:37,560 --> 01:08:39,160
Which is to stop looking outside.

593
01:08:39,185 --> 01:08:41,686
But look inside, look into your own heart.

594
01:08:46,722 --> 01:08:48,122
Be true to yourself.

595
01:08:48,147 --> 01:08:49,107
And the answer shall come.

596
01:09:04,125 --> 01:09:05,389
Xiaozhi!

597
01:09:12,800 --> 01:09:13,920
Xiaozhi!

598
01:09:16,798 --> 01:09:17,558
Chen Li!

599
01:09:18,598 --> 01:09:19,998
Chen Li!

600
01:09:56,436 --> 01:09:58,200
Aren't you afraid of catching a cold
when you swim on a rainy day?

601
01:09:58,200 --> 01:09:59,092
It's none of your business.

602
01:10:01,760 --> 01:10:03,061
Are you going to Chen Li's wedding?

603
01:10:06,206 --> 01:10:06,966
When?

604
01:10:07,647 --> 01:10:08,960
The 19th of next month.

605
01:10:08,960 --> 01:10:10,560
I'll pick you up on the way
if you want to go.

606
01:10:13,080 --> 01:10:13,880
Talk about it later.

607
01:10:17,763 --> 01:10:20,363
Are you going to my graduation
ceremony next week?

608
01:10:43,045 --> 01:10:43,826
Xiaolong,

609
01:10:44,521 --> 01:10:47,321
teacher Da Xiong sent several boxes
of lychees from the island.

610
01:10:47,346 --> 01:10:48,631
I'll send them to you and Xiaozhi...

611
01:11:01,936 --> 01:11:02,717
Xiaolong,

612
01:11:03,108 --> 01:11:05,880
teacher Da Xiong sent several boxes
of lychees from the island.

613
01:11:05,905 --> 01:11:07,185
They were all sent to me.

614
01:11:07,836 --> 01:11:09,569
I've been asked to deliver them
to you and Xiaozhi.

615
01:11:35,960 --> 01:11:46,560
(Just leave it with you.
I'll drop by to pick it up on my way.)

616
01:12:24,360 --> 01:12:24,720
Hello!

617
01:12:24,720 --> 01:12:26,015
Teacher Daxiong sent two boxes of lychees.

618
01:12:26,040 --> 01:12:27,015
- I'll give you a box.
- I don't need that.

619
01:12:27,040 --> 01:12:28,120
Keep it for yourself.

620
01:12:55,820 --> 01:12:56,492
Hello.

621
01:12:56,640 --> 01:12:57,680
Did you send over the lychees?

622
01:12:57,705 --> 01:12:58,865
I asked someone else to deliver it.

623
01:12:59,598 --> 01:13:01,278
I knew you weren't that diligent.

624
01:13:01,636 --> 01:13:02,836
When are you going to move back home?

625
01:13:03,257 --> 01:13:04,440
I've already graduated.

626
01:13:04,440 --> 01:13:05,240
Mind your own business.

627
01:13:05,265 --> 01:13:06,342
Tell me the truth.

628
01:13:06,367 --> 01:13:07,787
Are you with that Li Shijia?

629
01:13:07,812 --> 01:13:09,080
Nope.

630
01:13:09,080 --> 01:13:10,382
Then why are you living in his store?

631
01:13:12,645 --> 01:13:13,925
I just saw your brother.

632
01:13:17,524 --> 01:13:18,924
He came to bring you lychees, right?

633
01:13:19,674 --> 01:13:20,474
Yeah.

634
01:13:38,732 --> 01:13:40,092
I've sent you the graduation photo.

635
01:14:07,366 --> 01:14:08,374
Xiaozhi.

636
01:14:19,460 --> 01:14:20,540
I might work overtime today.

637
01:14:20,565 --> 01:14:21,845
Look after the store yourself at night.

638
01:14:22,580 --> 01:14:23,140
I'm off.

639
01:14:40,574 --> 01:14:41,374
Chen Li?

640
01:14:43,381 --> 01:14:44,181
Xiaozhi?

641
01:14:44,604 --> 01:14:45,204
What a coincidence.

642
01:14:45,724 --> 01:14:46,964
Why are you waiting here for the bus?

643
01:14:48,640 --> 01:14:49,880
My car was sent for maintenance.

644
01:14:49,880 --> 01:14:51,359
So I'll take the bus to work today.

645
01:14:51,898 --> 01:14:52,820
Oh.

646
01:14:55,520 --> 01:14:56,906
The company is not too far away.

647
01:14:58,500 --> 01:14:59,740
Let me walk you there.

648
01:15:00,560 --> 01:15:03,000
Okay, it's just one stop away
from the company.

649
01:15:03,976 --> 01:15:04,760
Let's go.

650
01:15:15,822 --> 01:15:17,382
How's your work recently?

651
01:15:17,760 --> 01:15:18,480
It's quite good.

652
01:15:18,480 --> 01:15:19,560
My colleagues are all very kind to me.

653
01:15:21,760 --> 01:15:23,160
Let me know if you need anything.

654
01:15:26,145 --> 01:15:28,281
Xiaozhi, did you change your phone number?

655
01:15:28,920 --> 01:15:30,320
I changed after graduation.

656
01:15:44,335 --> 01:15:45,935
You just put "younger bro" as the name?

657
01:15:45,960 --> 01:15:46,968
Or what else?

658
01:15:56,406 --> 01:15:57,240
This is me.

659
01:16:49,046 --> 01:16:49,840
Since childhood,

660
01:16:49,865 --> 01:16:52,345
how have we learned what "love" is?

661
01:16:52,960 --> 01:16:54,960
Is it the self disguised
under social labels?

662
01:16:55,440 --> 01:16:58,560
Or is it the sincerity radiating
from our true inner selves?

663
01:17:00,038 --> 01:17:01,598
In the process of stripping
away the disguise.

664
01:17:02,523 --> 01:17:04,445
I've been constantly striving
to get rid of fear.

665
01:17:04,470 --> 01:17:06,110
However, I can't overcome
the instincts of the flesh.

666
01:17:06,240 --> 01:17:10,742
My heart still beats nervously
on the verge of its endurance limit.

667
01:17:11,600 --> 01:17:15,800
It's just like the moment when a fish
in the water bites the hook and is lifted up.

668
01:17:16,809 --> 01:17:18,169
He should be the same as me.

669
01:17:18,880 --> 01:17:21,249
Suffering yet passionate.

670
01:17:40,080 --> 01:17:42,943
Xiaozhi, you don't look like your brother.

671
01:17:43,500 --> 01:17:44,900
My brother is straight.

672
01:17:45,023 --> 01:17:46,764
Just stop having designs on him.

673
01:17:46,789 --> 01:17:48,149
I'm not having designs on your brother.

674
01:17:49,686 --> 01:17:50,806
I am a 0.5.

675
01:17:51,148 --> 01:17:51,988
We have the same preference.

676
01:17:52,133 --> 01:17:54,773
0.5 plus 0.5 equal to 1, right?

677
01:17:58,224 --> 01:18:01,180
Bro, Li Shijia took the lychees
and gave them away.

678
01:18:01,205 --> 01:18:02,965
When will you send me another box?

679
01:18:04,080 --> 01:18:05,320
I don't have time to send it to you.

680
01:18:05,481 --> 01:18:06,496
Go to Chen Li.

681
01:18:08,216 --> 01:18:09,942
When did I give away your lychee?

682
01:18:10,865 --> 01:18:11,560
Now!

683
01:18:23,440 --> 01:18:24,520
(Damn!)

684
01:18:24,520 --> 01:18:26,960
(I hadn't eaten many
before my roommate gave them away.)

685
01:18:28,640 --> 01:18:30,200
(I'll send you another box.)

686
01:18:47,525 --> 01:18:48,325
Hello.

687
01:18:49,520 --> 01:18:50,396
Xiaozhi.

688
01:18:51,699 --> 01:18:52,499
Yeah.

689
01:18:53,118 --> 01:18:55,158
Do you have time tomorrow evening?

690
01:18:55,964 --> 01:18:56,964
Let's eat together.

691
01:20:02,965 --> 01:20:04,725
Did you just ask me to have dinner
together tomorrow?

692
01:20:06,640 --> 01:20:08,346
Actually, you can call me.

693
01:20:09,600 --> 01:20:10,385
Well.

694
01:20:11,960 --> 01:20:12,680
No time!

695
01:20:14,213 --> 01:20:15,408
Xiaozhi!

696
01:20:18,519 --> 01:20:19,519
Are you getting married next month?

697
01:20:23,308 --> 01:20:24,148
There's no wedding.

698
01:20:26,076 --> 01:20:27,516
Did you want to trick me into coming to
you on my own initiative?

699
01:20:30,260 --> 01:20:31,940
I'm not sure about your feelings.

700
01:20:48,825 --> 01:20:50,002
Can you forget?

701
01:20:50,875 --> 01:20:52,221
Those that have existed.

702
01:20:55,800 --> 01:20:57,182
I can't forget it.

703
01:21:00,033 --> 01:21:02,753
You can't forget it, so can I?

704
01:21:23,378 --> 01:21:24,738
Existence is just existence.

705
01:21:26,960 --> 01:21:28,205
It is neither right nor wrong.

706
01:21:28,838 --> 01:21:29,930
And it's neither reasonable or unreasonable.

707
01:21:29,955 --> 01:21:30,915
I know.

708
01:21:33,440 --> 01:21:35,240
You already taught me.

709
01:21:39,429 --> 01:21:40,429
It's just that I was too stupid.

710
01:21:59,196 --> 01:22:02,580
It took me three years to have the courage to face you.

711
01:22:14,632 --> 01:22:18,697
Fortunately, it's only been three years.

712
01:23:11,334 --> 01:23:14,465
Didn't you say you wouldn't come to
this year's summer camp?

713
01:23:16,240 --> 01:23:19,817
Not coming to the summer camp
doesn't mean not coming to see you.

714
01:23:21,400 --> 01:23:22,528
Assistant Nie!

715
01:23:24,238 --> 01:23:24,918
Here!

716
01:23:25,520 --> 01:23:26,551
Why are you shouting?

717
01:23:27,640 --> 01:23:28,489
Let's go!

718
01:23:31,517 --> 01:23:32,117
One!

719
01:23:33,000 --> 01:23:33,600
Two!

720
01:23:34,720 --> 01:23:35,418
Three!

721
01:23:41,247 --> 01:23:46,754
"Secrets Happened on the Litchi Island."

722
01:26:00,240 --> 01:26:02,040
They are too noisy on rainy days.

723
01:26:03,640 --> 01:26:05,000
Genetically speaking.

724
01:26:05,474 --> 01:26:08,280
Toads usually croak louder
in this kind of weather.

725
01:26:09,320 --> 01:26:10,755
It's their...

726
01:26:13,825 --> 01:26:15,122
reproductive behavior.

727
01:26:15,169 --> 01:26:16,724
Why are you looking at me
while saying that?

728
01:26:26,211 --> 01:26:31,594
(You're the best in your own world)
